# Pokémon Pack Opening Game

Open packs, collect Pokémon cards, track achievements, and manage your collection!

## Features
✅ Pack opening with rarity weighting  
✅ Collection binder with progress tracking  
✅ Achievements with notifications  
✅ Sell duplicates and selected cards for coins  
✅ Dark themed, responsive, and lightweight

## Usage
### Uploading to GitHub via Website
1. Go to [github.com](https://github.com/) and create a new repository (e.g., `pack-opening-game`).
2. On your computer, locate this project folder.
3. On the GitHub repo page, click **"Add file" → "Upload files"**.
4. Drag and drop all files and folders from this project into the upload area.
5. Scroll down and click **"Commit changes"** to upload.

### (Optional) Enable GitHub Pages
1. In your GitHub repo, go to **Settings** → **Pages**.
2. Under "Build and deployment", select the branch (usually `main` or `master`) and (if needed) set the folder to `/root` or `/docs` as appropriate.
3. Click **"Save"**. After a few moments, your game will be live at the provided URL!